stimulus:
Welcome to our experiment!

At the bottom of this screen, you will see a button that says 'Begin Experiment.
Please only click that button when you are ready to complete the 25 minute experiment in one sitting.

Once you click that button, it will not be possible to restart the experiment.

Welcome!

This experiment involves two parts: demographic information, followed by the experimental task.

It will take about 25 minutes to complete both parts.

In each trial of this task, you will see three texture images: one target item on top, and two choices beneath the target item.

Please select the item that is most like the target item.

To select the option on the LEFT, press the LEFT ARROW key. To select the option on the RIGHT, press the RIGHT ARROW key.

You are now ready to begin the experiment.

There will be around 200 trials. You will have opportunities to take breaks at three stages of the trials.
